parameters: Reporter: "Are you all watching this?"

Reporter: "In front of me is what appears to be a monster known as
Zaidag, and Pony Celes..."

Pony Celes, crucified by tentacles that sprang from the ground. The
people held their breath as they watched the scene unfold.

The reason they had gathered was because Octodag had announced through
the media that there would be an event involving Pony Celes.

Curious about what kind of event it could be, the general public and
TV crews gathered, gasping at the sight of the captive Pony Celes.

Octodag: "Really, everyone looks so bored... Can't you imagine what's
about to start?"
Fuminori: "This is an execution, isn't it..."
Junya: "Yeah... What else could this be but an execution..."

Octodag: "Oh dear, you guys don't understand at all. Why would I
execute Pony Celes, whom I love?"

Octodag: "We're about to have a wonderful event, so make sure you
broadcast it properly! You want good ratings, don't you?"
Reporter: "Of, of course..."
The reporters nodded in response to Octodag's words.

Despite the ethical issues, no one had the courage to shake their head
in front of the monster before them.
Octodag: "Well, it's about time."
Octodag: "Let's broadcast our love all over Japan!"
